      "height": 80,
      "text": "**Glass Interposer**\nSchott（德）/ Corning（美）/ LPKF"
    },
    {
      "id": "abf-header",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1020,
      "y": 440,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "**High-end ABF 基板**\n产能极度紧张\n扩产周期 3-5 年"
    },
    {
      "id": "abf-ibiden",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1020,
      "y": 540,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "**揖斐电 Ibiden**\nFC-BGA 全球第一\n极度紧张，优先英伟达/AMD"
    },
    {
      "id": "abf-shinko",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1020,
      "y": 640,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "**新光电气 Shinko**\n日本品质 + 散热方案\n产能有限"
    },
    {
      "id": "abf-unimicron",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1020,
      "y": 740,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "**欣兴 Unimicron**\nABF 快速扩产\n2026-2027 产能逐步释放"
    },
    {
      "id": "abf-taiwan",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1020,
      "y": 840,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "**景硕 Kinsus / 南亚 PCB**\n日月光体系 / 量产初期\n跟随扩产"
    },
    {
      "id": "cte-header",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1350,
      "y": 140,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 60,
      "text": "## 六、CTE 匹配挑战\n热膨胀系数失配 = 失效第一大根因\n\n2.5D/3D 堆叠核心壁垒"
    },
    {
      "id": "cte-table",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1350,
      "y": 220,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 220,
      "text": "**各材料 CTE (ppm/°C)**\n\n硅 Si：2.6\n铜 Cu：17\n陶瓷：6-9\n玻璃：3-8\n有机基板：15-25\nEMC：10-15\nUnderfill：25-45\n焊料：20-25\n\nCTE 失配 → 热机械应力"
    },
    {
      "id": "cte-failure",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1350,
      "y": 460,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "**热应力失效模式**\n• 界面分层\n• 焊点开裂\n• TSV 损伤\n• RDL 裂纹"
    },
    {
      "id": "rel-header",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1350,
      "y": 580,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 60,
      "text": "## Reliability Lab\n供应商审核必考维度\n\n7 大核心测试能力"
    },
    {
      "id": "rel-tests",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1350,
      "y": 660,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "**TCT 热循环** JEDEC-A104\n**HAST / PCT** JEDEC-A110\n**功率循环** 实际工况模拟\n**SEM / CSAM** 无损检测\n**DPA 破坏性分析** 截面\n**X-ray CT** 3D 重构\n**FEA 热机械仿真**\n**车规 AEC-Q100** 认证"
    },
    {
      "id": "rel-top",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1350,
      "y": 880,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "**头部供应商特征**\n✓ 内部 Reliability Lab（非外包）\n✓ 加速模型数据完整\n✓ AI/HBM 已量产记录\n✓ ISO 17025 认证"
    },
